credit_line: Gift of Sally Israel in memory of Fredericka Steinbach
title: Bracelet
provenance: With necklace 1996-35 1, belonged to donor's mother, Fredericka Steinbach; purchased by her in New York City in the 1930s.
description: Bracelet of 6 alternating rectangular, half-cylindric, blue/grey moonstones with beveled ends, each prong-set in backless silver frame, each frame flanked by small rectangles punctuated with marquesites; attached to each rectangle are semi-circular and circular links connected by decorative, oblong, marquesite-set elements; clasp recesses into rectangular element at opposite end, small lock mechanism attached to side of clasp.
name: Bracelet
